                <h2 class="intro-title">
                    Want to learn and don't know how and where?
                </h2>
                <p class="intro-info">
                    Welcome to <span class="learn-it">Learn It</span>. It is new learning web community, where you can learn together with your friends. Here you will find all kinds of courses for basically everything on the web. Come and join our big family and start learning now!
